library(forecast)
library(tseries)

close = HEPS[,5] #working on closed price

plot(close,type='l') #it is not a stationary time series

acf(close,main='ACF Plot',lag.max=100)

pacf(close,main='PACF Plot',lag.max=100)

auto.arima(close) #find appropriate values
## Series: close 
## ARIMA(0,1,3) with drift 
## 
## Coefficients:
##           ma1      ma2     ma3    drift
##       -0.0882  -0.1882  0.1845  -0.0920
## s.e.   0.0884   0.0894  0.0857   0.0341
## 
## sigma^2 estimated as 0.1805:  log likelihood=-67.86
## AIC=145.72   AICc=146.23   BIC=159.82
fit = arima(close[c(1:118)],order= c(0,1,3),include.mean = FALSE)

acf(fit$residuals)

arima.forecast = forecast(fit, h=3, level=99)

plot(arima.forecast)
